text: Anama hutege'za Mosese knafima korapa'ma fore'ma hu'nea zankura zamagesa ete nentahi'za amanage hu'za hu'naze. Hageri amu'nompima kama erifore huno vahe'ane naga'are'ma kegavama nehaza vahe'enema zamavareno'ma e'nea Anumzana iga mani'ne hu'za nehu'za, Agra Ruotage Avamu'ama atregeno amunozamifima enemanino,
